      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
                                   
        Game show in which four contestants compete for a cash prize in
        rounds that test their general knowledge and memory. In a 
        departure from the norm, while the questions are different, some 
        of the answers remain the same. Hosted by Terry Wogan 

